{"search_data": "BiharBihar Mukhyamantri SC / ST Udyami Yojana \u2013 Interest Free Loans to Entrepreneurs \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Bihar Mukhyamantri SC / ST Udyami Yojana 2020The minimum qualification under this scheme is Intermediate (Class 10th) for SC / ST candidates. The important features and highlights of Mukhyamantri Anusuchit Jati Evam Anusuchit Janjati Udyami Yojana are as follows:-Under CM SC / ST Entrepreneur Scheme, govt. will provide Rs. 10 lakh as financial assistance.Out of this total amount, Rs. 5 lakh would be given as Subsidy and Rs. 5 Lakh as Loan amount to the SC / ST entrepreneurs.No Interest would be charged on Loan amount. Rs. 5 Lakh Loan will be completely Interest free i.e entrepreneurs would not have to pay any additional amount during repayment.Under Mukhyamantri SC / ST Udyami Yojana, the entrepreneurs will have to make loan repayment in 84 equal installments.Repayment installment will begin only after the proposed industry or trade starts its operation.The process to get Interest Free Loans has been simplified. Loans will now be granted on Self Declaration by the beneficiary from any Nationalized banks.Bihar Anusuchit Jati Evam Anusuchit Janjati Udyami YojanaSC / ST members always faces difficulty in getting loans as Banks used to reject their applications on one pretext or other. This scheme will help them to avail loans from banks without any interest. This scheme will enable them to provide employment to other candidates. The state govt. is making every possible effort to improve the overall living standards of the people from weaker sections of the society. Bihar govt. wants to include all the entrepreneurs from SC / ST community in mainstream.Industries Department has launched this scheme within 2 months after conceptualisation. Out of the total 3000 applications received, 500 beneficiaries have been selected. Out of these selected beneficiaries, 135 have already being trained and training for other 150 entrepreneurs will start soon. CM Nitish Kumar has given Rs. 5 lakh to 5 beneficiaries to mark the official launch of this scheme.Bihar CM SC / ST Udyami Yojana Online Application FormAll the SC / ST candidates who wish to avail the scheme can check the complete eligibility conditions and fill the SC / ST Udyami Yojana Online Application Form through the official Startup Bihar Website:- http://www.startup.bihar.gov.in/CMSCSTUDYAMI/Default.aspxHere candidates can make registration first and then fill the online application form to avail subsidy and interest free loans upto Rs. 10 lakh to start their own business.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}